{"tid":1428971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄國夫婦將小孩交予親戚託向後參加反政府示威  政府發聲明指兩人濫用權力，危害幼童生命， 會以法庭取消兩人當父母的資格","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:53:39.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96319a0f851fe3ad97af3596dd200e2148c7cc94","tid":1428971,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2421216/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8F%8DDQ%E3%80%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%20%E6%81%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%881%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%92%E6%92%AB%E9%A4%8A%E6%AC%8A%C2%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2421216%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%258F%258DDQ%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%2520%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%25881%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%2592%25AB%25E9%25A4%258A%25E6%25AC%258A%25C2%25A0&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=977f3029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2421216/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8F%8DDQ%E3%80%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%20%E6%81%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%881%E6%AD%B2%E5%85%92%E6%92%AB%E9%A4%8A%E6%AC%8A%C2%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲ 上周末莫斯科的反DQ示威，遭俄羅斯政府嚴厲打壓。<br />\n俄羅斯政府發聲明，指涉案父母在早前的遊行期間將其年幼兒子交予第3方人士，危害幼童生命，斥二人濫用父母權力，損害兒子利益，莫斯科市檢控辦已向法庭尋求取消該對夫婦當父母的資格。<br />\n<br />\n【俄羅斯反DQ】逾萬人促公平選舉 警察暴力清場拘800人<br />\n<br />\n有調查人員指該第3方人士是活躍示威者，曾以利用他人孩子從圍捕中甩身。<br />\n<br />\n面臨喪失兒子撫養權的普洛卡佐夫（Dmitry Prokazov）接受英國廣播公司（BBC）訪問，稱當日只是出街散步，因他們支持示威者反對不公平選舉的理念，故不覺得害怕。<br />\n<br />\n他稱期間遇到一群示威者，太太的親戚兼他的好朋友福明（Sergey Fomin）就在其中，攀談期間曾讓福明抱兒子。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起廣泛回響，莫斯科官員亦對檢控部門做法不滿，莫斯科兒童權益申訴專員布尼莫維奇（Yevgeny Bunimovich）直斥不可接受，指任何情況下都不應用兒童作政治威脅。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯人權理事會主席費多托夫（Mikhail Fedotov）亦稱，當局所講的第3方人士，可引伸至保姆、祖父母等人身上，直指先例一開，所有父母都受威脅。<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科民眾已連續兩周末上街，抗議當局取消反對派人士參選議員的資格，遭遇嚴厲打壓，大量示威者事後被捕。"},{"pid":"0aadf99de844c57b54285b54680610b512dd9608","tid":1428971,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c672bd881315b874e224d3365b0776b73455ed19","tid":1428971,"uid":6222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"父母都有得dq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fe849f48663f37eb2387d1e631a9f0a0c638ac","tid":1428971,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3163a18e77fd581ecab8554a36fc005261eb1e","tid":1428971,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"暴政下的同路人"},{"pid":"0c08ff3a7f5e9189bd4aedadc27199404164ee44","tid":1428971,"uid":195258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"之前有連登仔吹奏普京<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1970aa8c19d9cc8943dbaac93516c554422b94cf","tid":1428971,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c672bd881315b874e224d3365b0776b73455ed19","tid":1428971,"uid":6222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"父母都有得dq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"唔爭氣笑咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7fad65318888eddd70f5b06c7fb2f2a1db1fb1","tid":1428971,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c08ff3a7f5e9189bd4aedadc27199404164ee44","tid"